                        <interp inst="t18630406-603-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">The prisoner was further charged with having been before con<lb></lb>victed of felony at Marylebone Police Court, on the</hi> 25<hi rend="italic">th May</hi>, 1857, <hi rend="italic">in the name of <persName id="t18630406-name-295">
                        <interp inst="t18630406-name-295" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
