                        <interp inst="t18630406-name-295" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>William Stewart</persName>, and sentenced to Six Months imprisonment; to this he</hi>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">PLEADED GUILTY</hi>.</p>
